snippet.title: UNDERTALE Nintendo Switch Release Trailer
snippet.description:
It's UNDERTALE for Nintendo Switch! Available September 18, 2018!

For more info, visit: http://www.undertale.com

Trailer by Everdraed + Fangamer
3D by Chelsea Saunders
Opening Animation by Temmie Chang
